genresAdvancedInfo.name: cumbia surena
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Cumbia Sureña is a popular genre in Peru and other parts of South America. It is known for its slower tempo, use of accordion and guitar, and incorporation of traditional Andean rhythms. Cumbia Sureña often features lyrics about love, heartbreak, and social issues.
